OL,3,C127 councils could collapse - with
OL,4,Cthose in the North of England most at
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FAnalysis shared exclusively with ITV
OL,8,FNews has laid bare the scale of the
OL,9,Ffunding crisis for councils and
OL,10,Fexposed large regional divides in
OL,11,Fbudgets and spending
OL,13,FCouncils across the North of England
OL,14,Fare almost twice as likely to fail
OL,15,Ffinancially within the next year as
OL,16,Fthose in the South - according to an
OL,17,Fexclusive analysis for ITV News.
