OL,3,C127 councils could collapse - with
OL,4,Cthose in the North of England most at
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FIt reveals that 30% of northern
OL,8,FCouncils could be at risk of financial
OL,9,Ffailure during the next 12 months -
OL,10,Fwith 55% at risk within five years.
OL,12,FThat compares to 17% in the first year
OL,13,Ffor those in the South of England,
OL,14,Frising to 35% within five years,
OL,15,Faccording to the research by Grant
OL,16,FThornton, published a week before the
OL,17,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt announces his
OL,18,Flatest budget.
