OL,4,Cthose in the North of England most at
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FAltogether the study suggests that 127
OL,8,Fcouncils in England - out of a total
OL,9,Fof 313 - could face financial failure
OL,10,Fbefore the end of the decade.
OL,12,FITV News' Deputy Political Editor
OL,13,FAnushka Asthana takes us through the
OL,14,Fanalysis
OL,16,FThe study paints a bleak picture for
OL,17,Flocal government - in which demand for
OL,18,Fservices is far outstripping levels of
OL,19,Ffunding across the country, leaving
OL,20,Fmore and more councils facing the
OL,21,Fprospect of a black hole.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/15
