OL,7,FThe report also finds that the
OL,8,Fpressures are most intense in urban
OL,9,Fareas - covered by unitary and
OL,10,Fmetropolitan councils that provide all
OL,11,Fservices to residents, including
OL,12,Fhousing, adult social care and
OL,13,Fchildren services.
