OL,7,FAnd it suggests the squeeze on
OL,8,Fcouncils remains, despite an
OL,9,Fadditional #600m injection of cash
OL,10,Ffrom government this year. That money
OL,11,Fhas been welcomed by many in the local
OL,12,Fgovernment sector, but figures tell me
OL,13,Fthat it is still a sticking plaster,
OL,14,Fwith much bigger, long-term reforms
OL,15,Fneeded to stem the funding crisis
OL,16,Ffaces councils.
