OL,7,FIt comes as the Local Government
OL,8,FAssociation publishes two surveys -
OL,9,Fone carried out in January this year,
OL,10,Fand then a second in February
OL,11,Ffollowing the announcement of extra
OL,12,Fcash.
OL,14,FIt finds that despite the additional
OL,15,Ffunding, the vast majority of councils
OL,16,F(85%) are still anticipating the need
OL,17,Fto make cost savings to set their
OL,18,Fbudgets - with seven out of 10 dipping
OL,19,Finto their reserves.
