OL,7,FThat echoes the findings of the Grant
OL,8,FThornton study - that dives into the
OL,9,Fdata to reveal how money is being
OL,10,Fdiverted from "discretionary" cultural
OL,11,Fservices - as well as roads and
OL,12,Ftransport - towards adult social care
OL,13,Fand children services, which councils
OL,14,Fare required by law to deliver.
