OL,7,FEven with the cuts, it reveals just
OL,8,Fhow precarious the situation is for
OL,9,Fcouncils - after Birmingham City
OL,10,FCouncil, Thurrock, Croydon and Slough
OL,11,Fissued section 114 notices -
OL,12,Feffectively declaring bankruptcy and
OL,13,Fforcing them to slash all non
OL,14,Fessential spending.
