OL,7,FThe authors define financial failure
OL,8,Fas a council's reserves falling to
OL,9,Fbelow 5% of their net revenue
OL,10,Fexpenditure - and find that 41% of
OL,11,Flocal authorities in England will find
OL,12,Fthemselves in that position by 2028/29
OL,13,Fif urgent action is not taken.
