OL,7,FDelving into specific services, the
OL,8,Fauthors reveal a steep decline in real
OL,9,Fterms spending on libraries, falling
OL,10,F17% across the country. London has the
OL,11,Fbiggest decline (27%) but also
OL,12,Fcontinues to have the highest per
OL,13,Fcapital spending levels when it comes
OL,14,Fto libraries.
