OL,7,FThe report reveals that Kensington and
OL,8,FChelsea Council spends #37 per head on
OL,9,Flibraries, the highest level in the
OL,10,Fcountry, followed by #28 in Camden and
OL,11,FHackney. At the other end of the scale
OL,12,Fis Cornwall spending just #3 a head,
OL,13,Ffollowed by Luton and Leicester, on #4.
