OL,7,FOverall, Grant Thornton suggest that
OL,8,F63 councils could face financial
OL,9,Ffailure over the next year, rising to
OL,10,F127 councils over five years. In terms
OL,11,Fof raw numbers that equates to 33 in
OL,12,Fthe Norther of England, 29 in the
OL,13,FMidlands, 13 in London and 52 in the
OL,14,FSouth. But proportionally - it is the
OL,15,Fnorth that looks set to be worst hit.
